A long rest. Lots of snakes.

328
00:53:54,488 --> 00:53:57,335
快到酒吧间去。你会更安全。
Get on over to the saloon. You'll be a lot safer.

329
00:54:11,222 --> 00:54:12,253
神的母亲!
Mother of God!

330
00:54:20,824 --> 00:54:22,378
佩德罗! 佩德罗!
Pedro! Pedro!

331
00:54:24,233 --> 00:54:25,728
