Let's bring him into the saloon.

333
00:54:29,453 --> 00:54:30,521
小心。
Careful.

334
00:55:02,469 --> 00:55:03,608
胡安! 爱马仕!
Juan! Hermes!

335
00:55:18,092 --> 00:55:19,550
把他放在地板上。
Put him down on the floor.

336
00:55:36,428 --> 00:55:38,264
他们说你是医生。好吗?
They say you are a doctor. Well?

337
00:55:39,732 --> 00:55:41,391
