Maybe you can do something.

338
00:55:42,097 --> 00:55:43,902
我不希望他死。
I would not like him to die.

339
00:55:44,777 --> 00:55:46,794
听。它不是汉密尔顿。
Listen. It wasn't Hamilton.

340
00:55:47,491 --> 00:55:48,915
