It was a monster.

341
00:55:51,633 --> 00:55:52,735
从地狱!
From hell!

342
00:55:55,842 --> 00:55:56,910
佩德罗!
Pedro!

343
00:55:57,476 --> 00:55:58,505
佩德罗!
Pedro!

344
00:55:59,388 --> 00:56:00,635
你不能死。
You mustn't die.

345
00:56:01,511 --> 00:56:02,578
不。
No.

346
00:56:03,355 --> 00:56:05,373
