Give me some whiskey for my men! The need it!

348
00:56:10,801 --> 00:56:12,676
他们认为有一个怪物。
They think there is a monster.

349
00:56:13,378 --> 00:56:15,001
我说没有。
I say there is not.

350
00:56:16,961 --> 00:56:18,726
这是一个悲惨的人。
It is one miserable man.

351
00:56:19,569 --> 00:56:22,274
我希望和他面对面地见面。去找他!
I wish to meet him face to face. Go find him!

352
00:56:24,751 --> 00:56:26,484
把它发给那些人。
Pass thit out to the men.

353
00:56:32,303 --> 00:56:35,044
