And pass the order to the rest of them to meet me in front of the ranch.

354
00:56:44,341 --> 00:56:46,215
你能给我留一个吗?
Would you leave one for me!

355
00:56:57,561 --> 00:56:58,804
你想要钱?
You wanna be paid?

356
00:56:59,195 --> 00:57:03,918
别告诉我你担心阿库姆巴没有足够的钱来买几瓶臭气熏天的酒。
Don't tell me you're afraid that Acombar haven't got enough money to pay for a few stinking bottles.

357
00:57:05,111 --> 00:57:07,650
你可以把这个放下。这是覆盆子糖浆。
You can leave this one behind. It's raspberry syrup.

358
00:57:08,278 --> 00:57:11,054
嗯好吧... 树莓糖浆不是我们...
Yeah okay... Raspberry syrup isn't what we...

359
00:57:16,733 --> 00:57:20,694
我希望真的是加里。这样他至少少了一个人。
I hope it's really Gary. This way at least he'll have to fight with one less.

360
00:57:21,359 --> 00:57:22,947
即使他们为此杀了我。
Even if they shoot me for it.

361
00:57:47,627 --> 00:57:48,695
抓住。
Catch.

362
00:57:52,429 --> 00:57:53,459
在这里。
Here.

363
00:58:09,476 --> 00:58:10,545
米盖尔!
Miguel!

364
00:58:13,094 --> 00:58:14,162
米盖尔!
Miguel!

365
00:58:15,391 --> 00:58:16,530
米盖尔!
Miguel!

366
00:59:40,177 --> 00:59:41,208
爸爸。
Dad.

367
00:59:41,674 --> 00:59:43,548
加里·汉密尔顿想从你这里得到什么?
What does Gary Hamilton want from you?

368
01:00:32,504 --> 01:00:34,130
他在吗?
Is he inside?

369
01:01:32,104 --> 01:01:33,349
米盖尔!
Miguel!

370
01:01:40,347 --> 01:01:41,320
米盖尔!
Miguel!

371
01:01:43,793 --> 01:01:44,969
米盖尔!
Miguel!

372
01:01:46,855 --> 01:01:47,863
米格尔。
Miguel.

373
01:01:55,066 --> 01:01:56,205
米格尔。
Miguel.

374
01:02:23,698 --> 01:02:27,589
要么绑起来，要么把它撞倒! 别再响铃了!
Tie it up or knock it down! Stop that bell ringing!

375
01:02:47,845 --> 01:02:48,949
传教士,
Preacher,

376
01:02:50,211 --> 01:02:51,801
谁按的铃?
who rang the bell?

377
01:03:10,565 --> 01:03:12,225
米格尔。米盖尔!
Miguel. Miguel!

378
01:03:29,873 --> 01:03:30,941
牧师!
Preacher!

379
01:03:33,179 --> 01:03:34,425
是谁?
Who was it?

380
01:03:35,267 --> 01:03:36,856
我问他是谁!
I asked who was it!

381
01:03:37,840 --> 01:03:39,500
我要一个答案!
I want an answer!

382
01:04:57,477 --> 01:04:59,494
米格尔。米盖尔, 请。
Miguel. Please, Miguel.

383
01:05:23,015 --> 01:05:24,082
我们走吧!
Let's go!

384
01:06:20,631 --> 01:06:22,182
把那个铃铛弄掉!
Get rid of that bell!

385
01:06:35,488 --> 01:06:37,183
- 你在吗，奇科? - 是的!
- You out there, Chico? - Si!

386
01:06:44,603 --> 01:06:46,929
好吧，把它系紧，然后下来!
Well fasten it and then come on down!

387
01:08:12,591 --> 01:08:13,944
让开!
Out of the way!

388
01:08:16,141 --> 01:08:17,349
我们走吧!
Let's go!

389
01:08:17,879 --> 01:08:19,539
我们回牧场去吧。
Let's get back to the ranch.

390
01:08:26,264 --> 01:08:27,295
好吧, 来吧!
Well, come on!

391
01:10:58,928 --> 01:11:00,804
我在找你，汉密尔顿。
I was looking for you, Hamilton.

392
01:11:01,540 --> 01:11:02,997
为什么会发生大规模屠杀?
Why this mass killing?

393
01:11:03,556 --> 01:11:07,103
你为什么这么恨我父亲? 你想杀了他，对吧?
Why do you hate my father so much? You want to kill him, don't you?

394
01:11:09,508 --> 01:11:10,611
是的。
Yes.

395
01:11:18,831 --> 01:11:21,084
我没想攻击你，我没有武器。
I don't intend to attack you, I'm unarmed.

396
01:11:28,920 --> 01:11:30,996
我来是因为我想知道真相
I came 'cause I wanna know the truth.

397
01:11:39,915 --> 01:11:41,716
