I have to know the thruth!

398
01:11:45,169 --> 01:11:46,236
加里!
Gary!

399
01:11:49,066 --> 01:11:50,275
最后。
At last.

400
01:11:56,892 --> 01:12:01,235
我不能像你说的那样待在这里。我想帮你。这武器已经很古老了。
I couldn't just stay here like you said. I wanna help you. Now this weapon is mighty old.

401
01:12:01,381 --> 01:12:03,361
但即使是这样，它仍然足够好。
But even if it is, it still works good enough.

402
01:12:07,121 --> 01:12:08,855
只是阿库姆巴的儿子。
It's only Acombar's son.

403
01:12:20,691 --> 01:12:22,493
他想知道关于他父亲的真相。
He wants to know the thruth about his father.

404
01:12:26,849 --> 01:12:28,723
你觉得你能接受吗?
You think you can take it?

405
01:12:29,702 --> 01:12:31,506
我会告诉你整个事情的经过。
I'll tell you the whole story.

406
01:12:37,390 --> 01:12:38,706
你想听吗?
You wanna hear it?

407
01:12:41,565 --> 01:12:43,119
是的，我一定要听。
Yes, I must hear it.

408
01:12:44,663 --> 01:12:45,766
迪克!
Dick!

409
01:12:57,151 --> 01:12:58,253
迪克!
Dick!

410
01:13:01,049 --> 01:13:02,507
你看到我儿子了吗?
Have you seen my son?

411
01:13:07,207 --> 01:13:09,497
- 迪克在哪里? - 他没和你在一起吗?
- Where is Dick? - Isn't he with you?

412
01:13:10,547 --> 01:13:12,600
他出去追你了。他跟着你出去了?
He went out after you. He followed you out?

413
01:13:13,123 --> 01:13:14,367
你这个笨蛋!
You idiot!

414
01:13:15,941 --> 01:13:18,821
你应该阻止他的! 你应该知道的!
You should have stopped him! You know better than that!

415
01:13:19,976 --> 01:13:21,707
你应该阻止他的!
You should have stopped him!

416
01:13:23,559 --> 01:13:25,991
如果他有个三长两短，你会付出代价的!
You'll pay for it if somthing happens to him!

417
01:13:33,266 --> 01:13:35,321
去给自己找把枪。扔掉它!
Go find yourself a gun. Get rid of that!

418
01:13:48,540 --> 01:13:49,571
迈克!
Mike!

419
01:13:50,384 --> 01:13:51,416
迈克!
Mike!

420
01:13:55,116 --> 01:13:56,502
迈克! 迈克!
Mike! Mike!

421
01:13:58,140 --> 01:14:01,297
迪克进城去了。我要你带几个人去把他带回来。
Dick went into town. I want you to take some men and go bring him back.

422
01:14:01,377 --> 01:14:04,118
你在那里! 把马牵到后面的马厩里去，快点!
You there! Get those horses in the back barn, hurry up now!

423
01:14:06,457 --> 01:14:09,270
如果风车倒下了怎么办? 我们走吧, 那就动起来吧。
What if that windmill comes down. Let's go, move.

424
01:14:24,896 --> 01:14:26,213
他就在这里。
There he is.

425
01:14:36,795 --> 01:14:39,677
你疯了吗，一个人出去? 你怎么了?
Are you out of your head going out alone? What got into you?

426
01:14:41,109 --> 01:14:42,391
我们回家吧。
Let's go home.

427
01:14:44,450 --> 01:14:47,606
迈克，把这四个人留在这里。把剩下的送回牧场。
Mike, leave these four men here. Get the rest back to the ranch.

428
01:14:54,367 --> 01:14:55,683
他们已经走了。
They've gone.

429
01:14:56,174 --> 01:14:58,321
那孩子不可能告诉他你在哪里。
The kid couldn't have told him where you were.

430
01:14:58,749 --> 01:15:00,209
但听着, 加里...
But listen, Gary...

431
01:15:01,045 --> 01:15:02,884
你最好不要在这里待太久。
It's better if you don't stay here for long.

432
01:15:11,727 --> 01:15:14,645
- 你为什么进城? - 我想见加里·汉密尔顿。
- Whay'd you go into town? - I wanted to meet up with Gary Hamilton.

433
01:15:22,615 --> 01:15:23,931
得到它!
Get it going!

434
01:15:27,348 --> 01:15:29,187
街上一个人也没有了。
There's noone left on the street.

435
01:15:32,497 --> 01:15:35,001
他们一定在农场等你。听...
They must be waiting for you at the ranch. Listen...

436
01:15:36,254 --> 01:15:38,508
加里·... 我不了解你。
Gary... I don't understand you.

437
01:15:39,107 --> 01:15:41,777
如果你想知道真相我觉得你已经疯了。
And if you wanna know the truth I think you've gone right out of your mind.

438
01:15:42,239 --> 01:15:43,555
你什么意思?
What do you mean?

439
01:15:43,874 --> 01:15:46,900
我可不愿意像你那样，一分钟也不肯给那个小流氓解释。
I wouldn't have waisted a minute explaining to that young scoundrel like you did.

440
01:15:47,702 --> 01:15:50,336
你不知道他比他父亲强多少，对吧?
You don't know that he's any better than his father, do you?

441
01:15:50,452 --> 01:15:52,324
你有孩子。你知道我们的。
You have children. You know that our.

442
01:15:54,452 --> 01:15:56,525
我们的错误不应该落在他们身上。
Our faults shouldn't fall on them.

443
01:16:00,677 --> 01:16:01,746
加里。
Gary.

444
01:16:07,011 --> 01:16:09,027
玛丽和他一起在房子里。
Mary is there with him in the house.

445
01:16:10,247 --> 01:16:11,421
我知道。
I know.

446
01:16:43,299 --> 01:16:45,352
- 把它。- 不, 谢谢。
- Take it. - No thanks.

447
01:16:45,596 --> 01:16:47,742
我有这个。这是最后的决战。
I have this. This here's a showdown.

448
01:16:48,448 --> 01:16:49,552
祝你好运。
Good luck.

449
01:17:01,981 --> 01:17:03,511
嘿, 那边!
Hey, over there!

450
01:17:04,556 --> 01:17:06,253
我发誓我看到了什么。
I could've sworn I saw something.

451
01:17:08,453 --> 01:17:10,044
- 他在哪里? - 在这里。
- Where is he? - Here.

452
01:17:34,931 --> 01:17:36,103
进来吧。
Come on in.

453
01:17:46,620 --> 01:17:47,794
来吧!
Come on!

454
01:17:56,882 --> 01:17:58,305
环顾四周。
Look around.

455
01:18:00,710 --> 01:18:02,821
你自己好好看看。
Take a good look for yourself.

456
01:18:08,678 --> 01:18:09,994
看到了吗?
See this?

457
01:18:11,741 --> 01:18:13,235
所有这一切吗?
All of this?

458
01:18:20,054 --> 01:18:22,236
这就是加里·汉密尔顿。
This is what Gary Hamilton was.

459
01:18:26,735 --> 01:18:27,803
