Or would you prefer to...

463
01:18:46,705 --> 01:18:49,897
住在粪堆里... 像我一样,
live in a dung heap... Like I did,

464
01:18:50,809 --> 01:18:52,199
当我还是个孩子的时候?
when I was a boy?

465
01:18:55,992 --> 01:18:57,238
好吗?
Well?

466
01:19:00,586 --> 01:19:01,939
我将告诉你。
I'll tell you.

467
01:19:02,918 --> 01:19:04,377
你不会喜欢的，孩子。
You wouldn't like it, boy.

468
01:19:04,971 --> 01:19:07,639
别告诉我你不喜欢我给你的生活。
And don't tell me you don't like the life I've offered you so far.

469
01:19:09,599 --> 01:19:11,259
我和你想的不一样。
I don't think like you.

470
01:19:15,616 --> 01:19:17,206
你什么意思?
What do you mean?

471
01:19:18,192 --> 01:19:19,816
你拒绝这一切?
That you refuse all this?

472
01:19:22,017 --> 01:19:24,591
我和他谈过了。我知道真相。
I spoke with him. I know the truth.

473
01:19:32,110 --> 01:19:33,912
你对真理了解多少?
What do you know about truth?

474
01:19:35,137 --> 01:19:37,423
真相! 这是事实!
The truth! This is the truth!

475
01:19:48,844 --> 01:19:50,751
我们分头行动机会更大。
We'll have a better chance if we split up.

476
01:19:51,767 --> 01:19:53,261
我希望你能来。
I hope you make it.

477
01:19:53,854 --> 01:19:54,885
祝你好运。
Good luck.

478
01:19:56,983 --> 01:19:58,122
Johnathan!
Johnathan!

479
01:20:28,227 --> 01:20:29,781
他跟你说什么了?
What did he tell you?

480
01:20:30,176 --> 01:20:32,572
- 一切。- 比如什么?
- Everything. - Everything like what?

481
01:20:33,550 --> 01:20:36,468
一切都要知道。战争还没有结束
Everything there is to know. That the war wasn't over

482
01:20:36,924 --> 01:20:40,295
当你袭击那辆给联盟军运金子的马车时。
when you attacked that stagecoach carrying gold to the confederates.

483
01:20:40,404 --> 01:20:42,942
你和圣马尔韆兄弟。而你却把责任推到他身上
You and the Santa Mar韆 brothers. And you managed to put the blame on him

484
01:20:43,676 --> 01:20:45,822
通过在舞台上放置一些证据。
by planting some evidence on the stage.

485
01:20:47,816 --> 01:20:48,990
但后来...
But then...

486
01:20:49,519 --> 01:20:51,917
那晚他有完美的不在场证明。
He had a perfect alibi that night.

487
01:20:53,104 --> 01:20:55,498
他在这里。他和玛丽在这里。
He was here. He was here with Mary.

488
01:20:56,477 --> 01:20:57,722
但是你...
But you...

489
01:20:58,772 --> 01:21:00,542
