You convinced Mary to betray him.

490
01:21:02,287 --> 01:21:04,056
她撒了谎，他付出了代价。
She lied, and he paid.

491
01:21:05,350 --> 01:21:07,117
现在我知道他为什么要你死了。
Now I know why he wants you dead.

492
01:21:09,387 --> 01:21:13,207
唯一确定的是，我们必须在他杀了你之前，杀了他。
The only thing that's sure, it that we must kill him, before he kills you.

493
01:21:15,439 --> 01:21:19,604
