Frank, why?

499
01:24:27,072 --> 01:24:28,769
因为你想要的...
Because you wanted...

500
01:24:29,335 --> 01:24:30,959
有人可以向他开枪。
somebody to shoot at.

501
01:24:31,700 --> 01:24:33,290
待着别动，听到了吗?
Just stay put, hear me?

502
01:24:46,001 --> 01:24:47,732
待着别动，胡安尼托。
Stay put yourself, Juanito.

503
01:26:00,593 --> 01:26:01,802
不, 加里。
No, Gary.

504
01:26:11,449 --> 01:26:12,587
不!
No!

505
01:26:13,780 --> 01:26:14,848
不。
No.

506
01:26:20,771 --> 01:26:22,123
哦, 加里。
Oh, Gary.

507
01:26:23,102 --> 01:26:24,276
